data.description: Come check out this comfortable 4 bedroom, 2 bath house in Kirby!  No HOA!  Master bedroom is split from other three bedrooms.  Located close to shopping, restaurants, highways (including Loop 410, IH 10, IH 35) AND MAYRA'S Bakery(Owners Favorite!).  Large lot with two storage building which will convey.
